

= Transaction Support Analyst (Accounting Firm) - Career Pathways

This document outlines career progression for transaction support roles within the Deals/Transaction Services divisions of major accounting firms in Australia. Transaction support professionals assist clients with financial due diligence, valuations, and transaction advisory for mergers, acquisitions, restructurings, and capital raises.

